pageContext.claim: “There's a town in California where they actually tried to take over the town council. All illegal aliens running the town council.”
pageContext.analysis: This is fantasy. In 2015, officials in Huntington Park, Calif., appointed one undocumented immigrant to the parks commission and another to the health commission. Anyone familiar with the basics of local government knows that these boards aren't the same as the city council. There is no movement of undocumented immigrants trying to take over the town.
